    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1867-08-13T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1867-08-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="349"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d349">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr. de
                        Stoeckl</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <hi rend="italic"
                                >Washington</hi>,</placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1867-08-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">August</hi> 13, 1867</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to inform you that Brigadier
                    General Lo vell H. Rousseau has been appointed by the President the commissioner
                    on the part of the United States to receive from the commissioner appointed on
                    behalf of his Majesty the Emperor of all the Russias the territory ceded to the
                    United States by the treaty of the 30th of March last. A copy of the
                    instructions which have been given to General Rousseau for his guidance in
                    executing that trust is herewith communicated for your information and that of
                    your government.</p>
                <p>I avail myself of this occasion, sir, to offer to you a renewed assurance of my
                    most distinguished consideration.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WILLIAM H. SEWARD.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Mr. <hi rend="smallcaps">Edward de Stoeckl</hi>, <hi rend="italic">&amp;c.,
                            &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
